# Design Language Rules

## Palette
- Primary background: `#0d0d0d` (near-black)
- Body text: `#f5f5f5`
- Accent gold gradient: **from** `#ffcc66` **to** `#ff8800` — matches logo stroke

## Typography
- Headings: `"Playfair Display", serif`, weight 600
- Body: `"Inter", sans-serif`, weight 400

## Layout & Style
- Visual mood = **minimal art-gallery**; generous whitespace, no drop-shadows
- All sections full-width; max-width 1280 px for inner content
- Use Tailwind utilities; never inline `style=""`
- Images: grayscale by default (`filter grayscale`), colour on hover (`filter-none`)
- Hover highlights use the gold gradient on a 1 px underline or thin border—not full fills
- Logo file lives at `/assets/logo/logo.png` and should be lazily loaded

## Performance & Accessibility
- Ensure **WCAG AA** colour contrast; prefer `text-white/90` over pure white on dark photos
- Performance budget: **< 150 kB** total JS, **CLS < 0.1**, **LCP < 2.5 s** on 3G
